Test Case ID: TC-004

Title:
Verify user cannot log in when Username field is blank

Preconditions:
1. User is on the Sauce Demo login page.

Test Steps:
1. Leave the Username field blank.
2. Enter "secret_sauce" into the Password field.
3. Click the Login button.

Expected Result:
1. User remains on the login page.
2. User is not authenticated.
3. Access to the Inventory page is denied.
4. An error message saying "Epic sadface: Username and password do not match any user in this service" is displayed.
